      <h2>Beautiful and Authoritative Maps on Thousands of Topics</h2>
      <p>
        The Living Atlas is the foremost collection of authoritative, ready-to-use global geographic information ever assembled. The vast array of themed content in the Living Atlas enables the exploration of people and places throughout the world, as well as the natural and man-made influences that impact them. Experience the benefit of on-demand access to valuable maps, data layers, tools, services, and apps to help you achieve your goals. Always changing and evolving, like our world, the Living Atlas houses information that impacts lives.
      </p>
